OL,3,CFarmers facing uncertain future after
OL,4,CDuchy reveals plans to sell Devon land
OL,6,FPeople living in Bradninch, in Devon,
OL,7,Fhave told ITV News they are "shocked"
OL,8,Fand "outraged" after being told the
OL,9,FDuchy of Cornwall plans to sell the
OL,10,Festate's farmland, leaving farming
OL,11,Ffamilies facing an uncertain future.
OL,13,FThe Bradninch estate, near Cullompton,
OL,14,Fhas been part of the Duchy for
OL,15,Fcenturies and was inherited by Prince
OL,16,FWilliam after his father became King.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
