OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1775052666
OL,3,CFarmers facing uncertain future after
OL,4,CDuchy reveals plans to sell Devon land
OL,6,FThe portfolio of land property and
OL,7,Finvestments has reportedly been valued
OL,8,Fat more than #1bn, and provides Prince
OL,9,FWilliam with a private annual income
OL,10,Fof #23m.
OL,12,FMultiple farmers are understood to be
OL,13,Faffected by the move. Full details of
OL,14,Fthe plans are yet to be revealed.
OL,16,FA spokesperson for the Duchy said
OL,17,Ftenants are being offered the chance
OL,18,Fto buy their own land.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
