FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43403
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1775052666
OL,3,CFarmers facing uncertain future after
OL,4,CDuchy reveals plans to sell Devon land
OL,6,FMary Ryan and John Palmer, who have
OL,7,Flived in Bradninch for 35 years, said
OL,8,Fpeople are "furious" at the plans, but
OL,9,Fmany "are too frightened to talk about
OL,10,Fit."
OL,12,F"They don't know what this means for
OL,13,Ftheir livelihoods, about the roof over
OL,14,Ftheir heads. Many we have spoken to
OL,15,Fare just at a loss, and some are
OL,16,Ffurious."
OL,18,FThey added: "We know over the last few
OL,19,Fyears, farmers' lives have been made
OL,20,Fso difficult. The last thing they
OL,21,Fneeded was this."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43404
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1775052666
OL,3,CFarmers facing uncertain future after
OL,4,CDuchy reveals plans to sell Devon land
OL,6,F"It's absolutely outrageous the way
OL,7,Fit's been handled. People are really
OL,8,Fupset and worried about whether they
OL,9,Fmay become homeless."
OL,11,FResidents said they are also worried
OL,12,Fabout what the decision means for
OL,13,Fcommunity assets in the town, such as
OL,14,Fthe wetlands, allotments and football
OL,15,Fgrounds.
OL,17,FSteve Huxtable, chairman of Bradninch
OL,18,FFC, said: "For the football club, we
OL,19,Fhave four years left on the lease, so
OL,20,Fwe don't know what's going to happen
OL,21,Fto that.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43405
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1775052666
OL,3,CFarmers facing uncertain future after
OL,4,CDuchy reveals plans to sell Devon land
OL,6,F"We spent nearly #100,000 building a
OL,7,Fnew changing room, and how that works
OL,8,Fout in the future, we just don't know."
OL,10,FThe Tenant Farmers Association said it
OL,11,Fis disappointed at the decision taken
OL,12,Fby the Duchy, but understands the
OL,13,Freasons behind it.
OL,15,FChief executive of the Tenant Farmers
OL,16,FAssociation, George Dunn, said: "Our
OL,17,Fjob is to work with the Duchy of
OL,18,FCornwall and the farmers, so when
OL,19,Fthings like this do happen, we can
OL,20,Fensure it's fair and reasonable for
OL,21,Fall."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
