OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1775052666
OL,3,CFarmers facing uncertain future after
OL,4,CDuchy reveals plans to sell Devon land
OL,6,FIn a statement, the Duchy of Cornwall
OL,7,Fsaid: "Our priority is to support
OL,8,Fevery tenant through this process with
OL,9,Fcare and respect.
OL,11,F"All tenants are being offered first
OL,12,Frefusal to purchase their homes and
OL,13,Ffarms, often with a discount,
OL,14,Falongside support to help them
OL,15,Fconsider what is right for them and
OL,16,Ftheir families.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
