OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43407
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1775052666
OL,3,CFarmers facing uncertain future after
OL,4,CDuchy reveals plans to sell Devon land
OL,6,F"More broadly, the wellbeing of our
OL,7,Ftenants is extremely important to us.
OL,8,FMental health support is available to
OL,9,Fall tenants, including a dedicated
OL,10,FFarming Mental Health Ambassador and
OL,11,Fspecialist support for farmers.
OL,13,F"This is a long-standing service that
OL,14,Fis always available, not just during
OL,15,Fthis process. We are committed to
OL,16,Fongoing, direct communication with our
OL,17,Ftenants and the local community as
OL,18,Fplans progress."
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/7
